<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>StoreJS — About</title>
    <style>
      @keyframes gradient { 0% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 50% { background-position: 100% 50%; } 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; } }
      body { background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #0d1117, #161b22, #1a1e2e, #0d1117); background-size: 400% 400%; animation: gradient 15s ease infinite; color: #c9d1d9; font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; min-height: 100vh; }
      h1 { color: #f0883e; }
      a { color: #58a6ff; text-decoration: none; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #238636; color: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; }
      .nav { margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; }
      .nav a { margin-right: 16px; }
      .card { background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 16px 0; }
      .tech { display: inline-block; background: #1f2937; border: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; margin: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
      .ascii { color: #58a6ff; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.2; white-space: pre; }
      .glow { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(248, 131, 62, 0.5); }
      .timestamp { color: #8b949e; font-size: 13px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="/products" class="btn">← Products</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <pre class="ascii">
   _____ _                    _ _____ 
  / ____| |                  | / ____|
 | (___ | |_ ___  _ __ ___  | | (___  
  \___ \| __/ _ \| '__/ _ \ | |\___ \ 
  ____) | || (_) | | |  __/_| |____) |
 |_____/ \__\___/|_|  \___(_)_|_____/ 
      </pre>
    </div>

    <h1 class="glow">About StoreJS</h1>

    <div class="card">
      <p>A demo product catalog for testing preview environments.</p>
      <p class="timestamp">Server time: <%= new Date().toISOString() %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="color: #f0883e; margin-top: 0;">Tech Stack</h2>
      <span class="tech">Node.js 22</span>
      <span class="tech">Express</span>
      <span class="tech">EJS</span>
      <span class="tech">DigitalOcean</span>
      <span class="tech">SuperPlane</span>
      <span class="tech">Nginx</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="color: #f0883e; margin-top: 0;">How it works</h2>
      <p>1. Open a PR on <a href="https://github.com/puppies-inc/storejs">puppies-inc/storejs</a></p>
      <p>2. Comment <code style="background: #1f2937; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">/start</code> on the PR</p>
      <p>3. SuperPlane spins up a DigitalOcean droplet with your branch</p>
      <p>4. Get a live preview URL in ~2 minutes</p>
      <p>5. Close the PR — environment auto-destroys</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
